Fowler went on to say: &quot;Like a lot of Liverpool fans, I&rsquo;ve yet to be totally convinced by Can and I reckon he really does need a massive end to the season if he is going to justify a &shy;significant pay rise. <br />
<br />
&quot;He&rsquo;s got promise, he&rsquo;s got &shy;obvious quality, but have we seen enough of it? He&rsquo;s a full Germany international who has been to major finals and he has also had two full seasons in the first team at Anfield, so, really, he can&rsquo;t hide behind the promising tag any more.&quot;

