Klopp on Can's contract: &quot;It makes no sense to talk about it. Emre likes to be here, we are in talks. We like him as a person and a player.&quot;

Yaya Toure is out of contract in the summer and his agent has said:<br />
<br />
&quot;A move to Liverpool, MUFC or Arsenal would be considered.&quot;

Wijnaldum: &quot;I think I&rsquo;ve surprised many people because I&rsquo;m showing I can still make the runs and get goals, but I&rsquo;m regaining balls.&quot;<br />
<br />
Wijnaldum: &quot;I am keeping the rhythm in the passing, covering for those around me and getting assists - seeing the complete version of me.&quot;

Klavan: &quot;I&rsquo;m a really quiet guy. My hobbies are my children. That&rsquo;s a full time job. My life is basically training &amp; family. I have 2 kids.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klavan: &quot;I am definitely a family man first. Definitely no, heavy metal, it&rsquo;s kids&rsquo; music, and Teletubbies!&quot;
